  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5699021/" class="title-link">明知不能胜的奋战  一曲悲壮雄浑的挽歌</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5699021"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36263556/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u36263556-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36263556/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">木木勺</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-15"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-15 12:35:55</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5699021_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  ◎木木勺  如果说《亮剑》还带有明显的传奇色彩，那么《大崩溃》无疑更加接近于真实的历史。这一次都梁没有再塑造李云龙式的孤胆英雄，而是讲述了惨痛沉重的豫湘桂大战。  一九四四年四月，豫湘桂之战中的豫中会战在河南打响，这是一场一开始就已注定了结局的战争。日军精心策...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
